divs: Sighting DetailsWell, Because I am writing a book on UFO photography, and I am almost finished the book, I decided to add a section of the book on submission of UFO pictures taken to various organizations. This picture was taken on October 29, 2009. So I am going through your photo and video submission process to capture how you folks want these things submitted. However, I have removed my personal information from the EXIF file part of the picture - making copies of the originals in the process - information on these two pictures, so the pictures will read that they were taken tonight.
